### Version
2.7.3

### Reproduction link
[github.com/Tofandel/vue-bug](https://github.com/Tofandel/vue-bug)

(That issue cannot be reproduced on codesandbox)





### Steps to reproduce
Use a functional component with both a static part and a dynamic part on vue 2.7.x

You can clone the reproduction, run `yarn install` and `yarn serve`
The page is not rendered, look at the error in the console

### What is expected?
No error to be thrown

### What is actually happening?
[Vue warn]: Error in render: "TypeError: _c is not a function"


---
I recently upgraded from 2.6.14 to 2.7.3

In vue 2.6.14 

```vue
<template functional>
  <div :class="classes">
    <p>{{str}}</p>
    <span><a>Hi bug</a></span>
  </div>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
    classes: null,
    str: String
  }
}
</script>
``` 
Used to compile to:
```js
var render = function (_h, _vm) {
    var _c = _vm._c
    return _c("div", {class: _vm.classes}, [
        _c("p", [_vm._v(_vm._s(_vm.str))]),
        _vm._m(0),
    ])
};
var staticRenderFns = [
    function (_h, _vm) {
        var _c = _vm._c
        return _c("span", [_c("a", [_vm._v("Hi bug")])])
    }
];
```

On vue 2.7.3 it compiles to:
```js
var render = function render(_c, _vm) {
    return _c("div", {
        class: _vm.classes
    }, [_c("p", [_vm._v(_vm._s(_vm.str))]), _vm._m(0)]);
};
var staticRenderFns = [function (_c, _vm) {
    return _c("span", [_c("a", [_vm._v("Hi bug")])]);
}];
```

The first parameter of [staticRenderFns is always `null` on both version](https://github.com/vuejs/vue/blob/main/src/core/instance/render-helpers/render-static.ts#L21), so it does seem obvious there is an issue in the compilation

